Text: RE Im Leaving EnronMary CONGRATS I wish you all of the best I enjoyed working with you and hope your new adventure suits you well Please keep in touch Cindy Cindy Tatham Recycling Project Specialist Washington County Solid Waste Recycling N First Ave MS Hillsboro OR fax Visit the Washington County website at wwwcowashingtonorusrecycle Visit the Business Recycling Awards Group BRAG website at wwwBRAGawardorg Visit the Waste Reduction Action Information Network WRAIN atwwwWRAINorg From SMTP Sent Friday March AM To KADDENCOM kaddencom WPPCorg Devon Kehoe TomO PAgov ernercom judy WPPORG MCIMAILCOM Subject Im Leaving Enron I am going to be the Senior Regulatory Counsel at ISO New England starting on April My last day in the Portland area will be March I enjoyed working with you and wish you the best of everything My new address will be Mary Hain Senior Regulatory Counsel ISO New England Inc One Sullivan Road Holyoke MA SONEcom
